auren-mayberry-launches-fun-freaky-sad-weird-joyful-solo-career-with-tour-3471192">她 2023 年个人头条巡演的欧洲站</a>，该巡演于本月早些时候访问了英国。 <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lauren-mayberry-live-koko-chvrches-madonna-spice-girls-review-photos-setlist-3512396">对她在伦敦 Koko 演出的四星评论</a>中写道：“这位 Chvrches 主唱独自闪耀，她用简短而尖锐的方式展示了她的个人时代。”</p><p>在巡演中，这位歌手还翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-madonna-and-debuts-solo-material-at-first-live-show-footage-setlist-3493492">麦当娜的《Like A Prayer》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-chvrches-lauren-mayberry-cover-the-1975s-paris-in-paris-3515964">1975 年的《Paris》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-texas-say-what-you-want-in-glasgow-3510404">Texas 的《Say What You Want》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-chvrches-lauren-mayberry-cover-pj-harveys-down-by-the-water-with-lo-moon-3509377">PJ Harvey 的《Down By The Water》等歌曲</a>。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lauren-mayberry-performs-chvrches-lungs-at-solo-show-for-bones-10th-anniversary-3504906">她还在多伦多表演了 Chvrches 的“OG deep cut”“Lungs”独奏版本，</a>以纪念三人组 2013 年首张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-chvrches-14808-321831">“The Bones Of What You Believe”发行</a>10 周年。</p><p>此外，这位创作歌手在今年的演出中展示了许多尚未发行的独奏曲目，包括“Change Shapes”、“Bird”和“Mantra”，以及她最近的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-makes-solo-debut-with-piano-ballad-are-you-awake-3491767">“Are You Awake？”</a>和 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-shares-new-single-shame-3512902">“耻辱”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-interview-solo-female-perspective-tour-album-future-3510639">梅伯里本月接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了她单飞的决定、摆脱</a>Chvrches 以纯粹女性视角写作的“自由”，以及对她尚未公布的首张专辑的期待。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-depeche-modes-personal-jesus-watch-video-3517631">Watch Chvrches 的 Lauren Mayberry 封面 Depeche Mode 的《Personal Jesus》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
